from mlee malcolm lee subject re a kind and loving god in article jmeritt write leviticu and the daughter of any priest if she profane herself by play the whore she profaneth her father she shall be burn with fire deuteronomy and the token of virginity be not find for the damsel then they shall bring out the damsel to the door of her father house and the man of the city shall stone her with stone that she die deuteronomy if a man be find lie with a woman marry to a husband then they shall both of them die deuteronomy if a damsel that be a virgin be betroth unto a husband and a man find her in the city and lie with her then ye shall bring them both out unto the gate of that city and ye shall stone them with stone that they die deuteronomy but if a man find a betroth damsel in the field and the man force her and lie with her then the man only that lay with her shall die these law write for the israelite god choose person whom god have expressly set apart from the rest of the world the israelite be a direct witnes to god existence to disobey god after knowing that god be real would be an outright denial of god and therefore immediately punishable remember these law be write for a different time and apply only to god choose person but jesu ha change all of that we be live in the age of grace sin be no longer immediately punishable by death there be repentance and there be salvation through my lord jesu christ and not just for a few choose person salvation be available to everyone jew and gentile alike god be with you malcolm lee 